Texts.Eng: Find the ^orange;artifact^reset; in ^green;the Dark Abyss Dimension^reset;

Texts.Chs: 在令人不安的^green;暗渊界^reset;中发现了^orange;深渊神器^reset;。通往那个空间的入口位于^#666666;黑暗深渊^reset;星球。
Texts.Eng: The ^orange;abyss artifact^reset; is found in the ^green;Dark Abyss Dimension^reset;, which is known for being extremely unsettling. Portals to this dimension are located in ^#666666;dark abyss^reset; worlds.
